snippet.title: Ice Cream Pachinly Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Ice Cream Pachinly comes out July 19th! 

Ice Cream Pachinly is a 3D top-down action game! Play as the hero Ice Cream Pachinly and battle the evil alien Glarg and his endless forces! Team up with a friend in split-screen CO-OP!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2861050/Ice_Cream_Pachinly/
